      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait temporal lobe tingling? i've never even heard of that. is that actually a thing? and you're sure it's just the pressure? it felt so much more intense than a normal migraine, like it was the worst pain i've ever felt in my life for a second. u think i really just need ibuprofen and water?",
